7f98133ae805f9eaf74c30d0e68d3a65b3e37f4c:
mutation EditGuildConfig($id: BigInt!, $patch: GuildConfigPatch!) {
  updateGuildConfig(input: {patch: $patch, id: $id}) {
    guildConfig {
      disabledChannels
      id
      inviteGuard
      joinMsg
      joinMsgEnabled
      joinReact
      leaveMsgEnabled
      leaveMsg
      logMember
      logMemberEnabled
      logMod
      logModEnabled
      logMsg
      logMsgEnabled
      maxMention
      msgChannel
      muteDmEnabled
      muteDmText
      muteDuration
      muteRole
      prefix
      roleChannel
      roleConfig
      roleEnabled
      warnDmText
      warnDmEnabled
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
1e31acedc3c6d9e88e2c03eb9e57fd54003ec3a5:
query GuildConfig($guildId: BigInt!) {
  guildConfig(id: $guildId) {
    disabledChannels
    inviteGuard
    joinMsg
    joinMsgEnabled
    joinReact
    leaveMsg
    leaveMsgEnabled
    logMember
    logMemberEnabled
    logModEnabled
    logMod
    logMsg
    logMsgEnabled
    maxMention
    msgChannel
    muteDmEnabled
    muteDmText
    muteDuration
    muteRole
    prefix
    roleChannel
    roleConfig
    roleEnabled
    warnDmEnabled
    warnDmText
    cachedGuildById {
      icon
      id
      name
      banner
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
f7225858e70ccfad9d31c2a71b8691cbd9bd234f:
query GuildRule($id: BigInt!) {
  guildRule(id: $id) {
    actions
    conditions
    enabled
    id
    createdAt
    name
    setId
    trigger
    updatedAt
    __typename
  }
}
